===Verb===
{{en-verb|loos|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To let loose, to free from restraints.
# {{transitive}} To [[unfasten]], to [[loosen]].
# {{transitive}} To make less tight, to [[loosen]].
# {{intransitive}} Of a grip or hold, to [[let go]].

====Usage notes====
